token_lists.title: CHX-Afterlife
token_lists.description:
A collection of 15 single edition artworks. Made up of upscaled and slightly edited test outputs from the CHX-1 algorithm released on fxhash on 17/03/22 https://www.fxhash.xyz/generative/10819 

About CHX-1: "Glitching pixels like it’s 1999. Inspired by 90’s digital aesthetics, CHX-1 takes a random selection of GAN seeds, combines them in unique ways, and processes them –individually and as a group– with a series of glitching dithering algorithms. Generating fun, original, colorful artworks."

GAN –> p5js –> Photoshop –> Blockchain

Thomas Noya • 2022

token_lists.title: COLOREAR
token_lists.description:
I have a feeling
When I am back in nature
When the sun shines bright
When the colors belong to each other
I remember home
I remember love
I remember care
I bring back that feeling whenever I can
And whenever I do,
I am.


COLOREAR is a series composed by 8 images. These images belong to an archive of photographs that I took between 2014-2015 while I traveled to Huancayo (Peru), to revisit my father’s hometown. These images resonate in a special way now that I became an immigrant.
The images are taken in black and white film roll, 6 x 6 format camera and haven´t been published before.
